_sText:
The first map I have released (not made), Just a GunGame map with lots of places for cover, containers to go inside.

It has 3 levels for playing on, Ground Floor, Mesh Walkway (2nd Floor), Roof (Extra storage loft space).

Fast paced and chaotic. Great to play.

Looking for any comment and improvemnts, And if your going to say some thing bad about it, say why so i can learn...
